+  console.error('Control error:', err);
+});
+```
+
+### Performance
+
+**UnixPipeAdapter:**
+- Throughput: ~500K msgs/sec (object mode)
+- Latency: <1ms (same machine)
+- Overhead: Socket + stream wrapping
+
+**UnixControlAdapter:**
+- Throughput: ~10K msgs/sec
+- Latency: 1-2ms
+- Overhead: JSON serialization + parsing
